Don't wanna close my eyes

1905
02:19:51,120 --> 02:19:55,193
l don't wanna fall asleep

1906
02:19:55,320 --> 02:19:59,029
Yeah, l don't wanna miss a thing

1907
02:22:56,480 --> 02:23:01,156
All my bags are packed
l'm ready to go

1908
02:23:01,240 --> 02:23:04,915
l'm standin' here outside your door

1909
02:23:05,040 --> 02:23:09,875
l hate to wake you up to say goodbye

1910
02:23:11,640 --> 02:23:15,792
But the dawn is breakin'
lt's early morn

1911
02:23:15,920 --> 02:23:19,435
The taxi's waitin'
He's blowin' his horn

1912
02:23:19,520 --> 02:23:22,717
Already l'm so lonesome

1913
02:23:22,840 --> 02:23:24,796
l could die

1914
02:23:26,560 --> 02:23:30,917
So kiss me and smile for me

1915
02:23:31,000 --> 02:23:34,515
Tell me that you'll wait for me

1916
02:23:34,640 --> 02:23:39,919
Hold me like you'll never let me go

1917
02:23:41,120 --> 02:23:45,671
'Cause l'm leaving on a jet plane

1918
